Welcome to our community! Please follow these rules to keep things friendly and fun:
Be Respectful and Safe: Treat everyone kindly. No harassment, hate speech, or sharing personal information.
Stay On-Topic: Use channels for their intended purpose and follow specific guidelines.
No Spam or Unauthorized Promotion: Avoid spamming or self-promotion unless approved in designated channels.
Follow Discord’s Guidelines: Adhere to Discord’s Community Guidelines (https://discord.com/guidelines). No NSFW or illegal content.
Cooperate with Moderators: Follow moderator instructions and resolve issues privately.